com.fns.grivet.model

Class ClassAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fns.grivet.model.ClassAttribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Auditable<String>, Serializable

    @Entity
public class ClassAttribute
extends Object
implements Auditable<String>
    A ClassAttribute expresses a three-way relationship between a Class.id, an Attribute.id and an AttributeType.id. A Class typically has one or more ClassAttribute.
    Author:
    Chris Phillipson
